cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category as the paper uses a maximum entropy classifier, which is a machine learning algorithm. 

cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible sub-category as the paper deals with identifying and annotating temporal expressions and relations in text, which is a task that is relevant to information retrieval.
